    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2 id=\"h_01H9TXQD5RM393P82P3Q1E9XTY\">Issue</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>I would like to change my Liferay account password.</li>\n<li>I would like to update my Liferay account information: company information, addresses, phone numbers, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_01H9TXQD5RN6Y4MS1RA375YJN4\">Resolution</h2>\n<p>Liferay customers are able to update their basic contact information through <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Customer Portal</a>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\">support.liferay.com</a> </li>\n<li>After signing in, expand your user menu<strong> </strong>(located in the top right corner)</li>\n<li>Click on <strong>Account Settings</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To update your Personal Information:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Click <strong>Edit Profile</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Re-enter your Liferay account password</li>\n<li>On the reloaded page, click <strong>Edit</strong> on the <strong>Personal Information </strong>table</li>\n<li>Make updates to your name, email, phone, and time zone<br>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-color-red110\"><em>Note<strong>: </strong>Phone numbers must be entered in the proper E.164 format:</em></span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-red110\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[+] [country code] [subscriber number including area code]</span></em></span>\n</li>\n<li><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-blue\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Note: For security purposes, free email addresses (example: xyz@gmail.com) are not allowed.</span></em></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To update your Password:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Enter your <strong>Current Password</strong> under the <strong>Change Password </strong>table </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Enter your New Password and Confirm New Password </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Click<strong> Change Password</strong></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To update your Display Language: </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Click <strong>Edit </strong>on the <strong>Display Language </strong>table</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Select the desired language from the drop-down field</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Click <strong>Save</strong></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Optionally, to update the display language, you can leverage the language selector on the site that you are currently visiting.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>"
      },
